data.description: Welcome to 22 Hockeborn. This very well maintained 3 bedroom 1 and a half bath home sits on a quiet dead end street. The recently refinished hardwood floors are beautiful and throughout the first floor. The main floor also includes a half bath and laundry room. The third floor offers three bedrooms as well as a recently remodeled bath and plenty of closet space. Outside you will find a covered deck as well as an above ground pool. The 2 car garage is insulated and heated. Please make an appointment today.
